social_posts.post_text:
Long Post Alert 😬

Creating content is hard…! 
It’s a full time job that requires commitment, consistency, organization, passion and creativity! 
And it doesn’t get any easier as a parent (of 3) with a full time job. 
However, we are living in a time where a social media presence is crucial for success and exposure no matter your field of work. 
Any excuse of why you don’t have a presence is just that, AN EXCUSE! 
Nothing worth having comes easy and hard work beats talent when talent doesn’t work hard. 
Remember to always stay true to yourself along the journey and focus on what you’re doing, not others. 
In the meantime, enjoy this video I shot at 8:00 pm after my class, tired from a long day or work and kids!
P.s normally I’m already getting ready for bed by 8 😂
